{"tid":1095851,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[強風吹拂] 青春到懷疑人生了...","createTime":"2019-04-07T10:12:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T15:44:44.000Z","uid":28823,"like":37,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4fd9a5c0e31e5edcc642013bf1ef240674d56044","tid":1095851,"uid":28823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T10:12:05.000Z","msg":"每個人跑既原因同意義都唔同，十個人既成長故事，佢地每人跑果段獨白睇到我眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n年青時立下創舉，果種經驗同感受，係幾咁令人....字窮唔知點印容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最寶貴係果種&quot;回憶&quot;，無論你搵幾多錢買左幾多層樓，都唔夠果種&quot;回憶&quot;珍貴...<br />\n日後就算窮到要訓天橋底賣屎眼，但一回想係依種回憶，內心都富有起來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係果種身心被填滿，充滿色彩，充滿朝氣既人生，係幾咁青春...<br />\n唔係每個人都做過既事，而你自己做到了，果種滿足感，係一生既...<br />\n<br />\n最緊要係，成班同伴一齊為目標而努力，果種友情，真係屌你老母好撚祟拜，想要想追求...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冷暖不再自知，有同伴一齊分享，一齊感受。<br />\n&quot;有人在等待我&quot; ，望圖都感受到咩叫 &quot;友情，熱血，青春&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sYw6bmC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsYw6bmC.jpg&h=028e814b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家都一齊經驗過，回憶中有大家存在，果種得來不易既友情，辛苦過後得到既成果...<br />\n&quot;有人在等待我&quot;  ，全男班最高，成班仔一齊為目標努力果下，唔係女性圈子可以感受到...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8V5OpH6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8V5OpH6.jpg&h=7dc5d4b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現在一齊跑，過去回想，將來前進...<br />\n睇到依張圖，我喊撚左，見到前輩跑係前面，回頭望住你笑...<br />\n啊，有種傳承既味道，薪火相傳既意志，一代傳一代，係生命......<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y771KKm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy771KKm.jpg&h=93ab8c1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n強風吹拂，真係屈機，講左好多人生道理<br />\n我最愛係 : 不再是寂寞孤獨，何為強? 強唔係第一，比賽唔係睇排名(所以我先一直都咁強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xPywnwQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxPywnwQ.jpg&h=2998bb48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟我係到做緊乜撚野，我對唔對得住自己既人生同青春...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eaf6e834405ddf2614d6a4fed8e1fe54fed8096","tid":1095851,"uid":49275,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T10:16:35.000Z","msg":"gay"},{"pid":"dc1f7de00f3a156eae9c9f12a141b3fc1b59575a","tid":1095851,"uid":46389,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T10:20:10.000Z","msg":"難得高質<br />\n正評左"},{"pid":"d7a1da68902cf6005d1aacc2b209b74a57c298fa","tid":1095851,"uid":4618,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T10:21:50.000Z","msg":"跑步意義就係真物"},{"pid":"fd71916d4801dfe695a66596096cff9d6c58e53d","tid":1095851,"uid":197836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T10:23:46.000Z","msg":"好唔好睇過果青"},{"pid":"0a9e01ce911daa9538c63e2d0e2899a3f7c733b0","tid":1095851,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T10:25:45.000Z","msg":"睇左頭兩集放底左<br />\n要睇番晒了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb3f76064a33a61443d5c6e7231e66358ba3e145","tid":1095851,"uid":28823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8eaf6e834405ddf2614d6a4fed8e1fe54fed8096","tid":1095851,"uid":49275,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T10:16:35.000Z","msg":"gay"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T10:30:44.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得依套野無女生參與係個比賽，真心好..<br />\n成班仔入面有女只會阻住哂，你望下果兩個孖生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c3900e38c464f48ca40882c128f485375cdbda","tid":1095851,"uid":28823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc1f7de00f3a156eae9c9f12a141b3fc1b59575a","tid":1095851,"uid":46389,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"cit